{"tid":1542463,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"提返大家，香港嘅Dark Age好快蒞臨","createTime":"2019-09-05T00:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T23:03:28.000Z","uid":61002,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9427a1688b59f622a8e530f7741ec9df4e426e","tid":1542463,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"自20190831之後，香港既有僅有嘅最後防線，已然崩壞:<br />\n1. 記者&amp;FA被驅逐<br />\n2. 黨鐵真正的誕生，而且啲新同事仔會講粗口<br />\n3. 私人場所被強行闖入，最新有巴士車廂<br />\n4. 開場放題，雖然都唔係新嘢<br />\n5. 平民會互相篤灰起底埋伏，不過恐怖份子只會對付某陣營<br />\n<br />\n就此，我宣告<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察係有特權係大撚晒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係未贏之前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw為此可能有需要調整一下目前嘅撚狗策略<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">諗諗計救下街坊師  think think how to save neighborhood<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537135</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"8c6e5c1779bb6a7053fac42e8c23916ecefb6883","tid":1542463,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e967390252ecbe7cd5e83e89fa21791a733004a","tid":1542463,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下星期一 9月9 大專罷課集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為大專生<br />\n今次開學罷課搞到咁柒<br />\n完全俾中學生比下去<br />\n知道大家好慚愧 好想付出更多<br />\n<br />\n短時間內嘅主題<br />\n係要美國國會通過香港人權法案<br />\n既然7號有塞機場 8號有美國領事館<br />\n點解我哋大專生<br />\n唔襯中學生9號一週一罷<br />\n一齊搞多次罷課集會<br />\n有聲勢浩大既民意表態<br />\n既可以團聚學界<br />\n又為之後嘅三罷打強心針<br />\n<br />\n7號8號9號 一連三日嘅大型示威集會<br />\n就可以show到民意支持<br />\n俾美國國會順利表決通過條人權法<br />\n<br />\n香港就快死啦<br />\n一齊撐住好唔好<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n洗版洗到有組織搞9月9罷課為止</span></span>"},{"pid":"4fbcd5d95680978be5cb5cc11b6a85616dd6a200","tid":1542463,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過埋今晚大家明未"},{"pid":"598316bcbea2cce93ba5c49dca2dd8fec9e05a72","tid":1542463,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自20190831之後，香港既有僅有嘅最後防線，已然崩壞:<br />\n1. 記者&amp;FA被驅逐<br />\n2. 黨鐵真正的誕生，而且啲新同事仔會講粗口<br />\n3. 私人場所被強行闖入，最新有巴士車廂(因為一直都未試過會截查巴士)<br />\n4. 開<span style=\"color: red;\">槍</span>放題，雖然都唔係新嘢<br />\n5. 平民會互相篤灰起底埋伏，不過恐怖份子只會對付某陣營<br />\n<br />\n就此，我宣告<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察係有特權係大撚晒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人自求多福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係未贏之前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw為此可能有需要調整一下目前嘅撚狗策略<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">諗諗計救下街坊師  think think how to save neighborhood<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537135</a></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c812c129ef45d2b56314bda00a7499dcda97a89f","tid":1542463,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2f915dcda788d14db466ea7bc732da11a39b95","tid":1542463,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2d39728bf0f6efb9d6b98383103e26ee5e5ba8"